---
import PatreonLogo from '../images/patreon-logo.jpg';
import Phead from '../images/phead.jpg';
---

<div class="patreon-info">
  <a class="patreon-img-link-block" href="https://www.patreon.com/mt_aiphotoproj" target="_blank">
    <img class="phead" src={PatreonLogo} alt="patreon-logo" />
    <img class="phead" src={Phead} alt="patreon-header" />
  </a>
  <div class="patreon-info-text">Sexy street photo is available on Patreon. It encourages us in our daily activities. Please support us.</div>
  <div style="margin-top: 5px;" class="patreon-info-text">PatreonにてSexy Street Photoを公開しております。日々の活動の励みになります。是非ご支援ください。</div>
</div>

<style>
  .patreon-info {
    font-size: 12px;
    width: 200px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: #606060;
  }

  .patreon-img-link-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .patreon-info-text{
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  .phead {
    max-width: 100%;
  }
</style>
